{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_看进山路",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·看进山路 + 夜路回程（两段式：恍然/变体/不容松手/成败分支）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "flow_xungou_main",
              "state": "s09_songhuo",
              "reached": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "done_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n1"
    },
    "done_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "不看了。那条路看人的时候，比人看它的时候多。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "棚子后头，那条进山的路扎进雾里，看不到第十步。两边的树静得不对——鸟都不落。",
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（过了岭，就是神仙顶……李天狗当年，走的就是这条道嗦？）",
      "next": "n3"
    },
    "n3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "盯着盯着，一股寒气顺着脊梁骨往上爬。他打了个寒颤，啐了一口，掉头就走——",
      "next": "n_night"
    },
    "n_night": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_看进山路",
            "signal": "songhuo_gazed"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "fadeWorldToBlack",
          "params": {
            "durationMs": 900
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "playScriptedDialogue",
          "params": {
            "lines": [
              {
                "speaker": "",
                "text": "脚帮在岭口就散了，各有各的去处。他独自往回赶。下山一半，天彻底黑透。"
              },
              {
                "speaker": "",
                "text": "回程的道，把去程那三个画X的地方，倒着再走一遍。林子里的虫鸣，一声一声稀下去——然后，没了。"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n_p3sig"
    },
    "n_p3sig": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "fadeWorldFromBlack",
          "params": {
            "durationMs": 600
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_看进山路",
            "signal": "hanming_ret_p3"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "sw_p3"
    },
    "sw_p3": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "wrap_喊名_点三",
              "state": "right"
            }
          ],
          "next": "p3r_call"
        },
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "wrap_喊名_点三",
              "state": "wrong"
            }
          ],
          "next": "p3w_call"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "p3q"
    },
    "p3r_call": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "林子里"
      },
      "text": "「二狗——」",
      "next": "p3r_tail"
    },
    "p3r_tail": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "一声。清清楚楚，从他喊过「黄秉文」的那条沟里飘出来。慢悠悠的，认得他的名。",
      "next": "sw_awk_p3"
    },
    "p3w_call": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "林子里"
      },
      "text": "「二狗——」「二狗……」「——二狗？」",
      "next": "p3w_tail"
    },
    "p3w_tail": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "好几个声音抢着喊。急，杂，一声压着一声，全从他喊岔了名的那条沟里涌上来。",
      "next": "sw_awk_p3"
    },
    "p3q": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "过那条沟的时候，只有风。他脚步没停。",
      "next": "sw_awk_p3"
    },
    "sw_awk_p3": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "not": {
                "narrative": "wrap_喊名_点三",
                "state": "skipped"
              }
            },
            {
              "narrative": "wrap_喊名_恍然",
              "state": "pending"
            }
          ],
          "next": "awk3_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n_p2sig"
    },
    "awk3_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（这声音——从我喊名的那点来的。）",
      "next": "awk3_2"
    },
    "awk3_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（那些名字……是喊魂。我一路喊，把它们喊、醒、了。要是还喊岔了名——认错了主，就全乱了。）",
      "next": "awk3_3"
    },
    "awk3_3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "脚帮那句话在耳朵里嗡嗡响：山里喊名，千万别应。应一声，魂就被勾了去。",
      "next": "awk3_sig"
    },
    "awk3_sig": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_看进山路",
            "signal": "hanming_awakening"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n_p2sig"
    },
    "n_p2sig": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_看进山路",
            "signal": "hanming_ret_p2"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "sw_p2"
    },
    "sw_p2": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "wrap_喊名_点二",
              "state": "right"
            }
          ],
          "next": "p2r"
        },
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "wrap_喊名_点二",
              "state": "wrong"
            }
          ],
          "next": "p2w"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "p2q"
    },
    "p2r": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "「二狗——」又一声，从隔坡那个画X的地方来。不急。像个熟人在等他回头。",
      "next": "sw_awk_p2"
    },
    "p2w": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "抢着喊的那几个声音，又起来了。这回，离得近——左边一声，右边一声，背后还有一声。",
      "next": "sw_awk_p2"
    },
    "p2q": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "隔坡那处，安安静静。只有他自己的脚步声，深一脚，浅一脚。",
      "next": "sw_awk_p2"
    },
    "sw_awk_p2": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "not": {
                "narrative": "wrap_喊名_点二",
                "state": "skipped"
              }
            },
            {
              "narrative": "wrap_喊名_恍然",
              "state": "pending"
            }
          ],
          "next": "awk2_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n_p1sig"
    },
    "awk2_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（这声音——从我喊名的那点来的。）",
      "next": "awk2_2"
    },
    "awk2_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（那些名字……是喊魂。我一路喊，把它们喊、醒、了。）",
      "next": "awk2_3"
    },
    "awk2_3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "脚帮那句话在耳朵里嗡嗡响：山里喊名，千万别应。应一声，魂就被勾了去。",
      "next": "awk2_sig"
    },
    "awk2_sig": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_看进山路",
            "signal": "hanming_awakening"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n_p1sig"
    },
    "n_p1sig": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_看进山路",
            "signal": "hanming_ret_p1"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "p1_a"
    },
    "p1_a": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "最后一个画X的地方到了——他自己亲口喊过「李长生」的那块林子边。",
      "next": "p1_call"
    },
    "p1_call": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "林子里"
      },
      "text": "「二狗——」",
      "next": "p1_b"
    },
    "p1_b": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "一声。清清楚楚。不远不近，就在林子第一排树的后头。",
      "next": "sw_awk_p1"
    },
    "sw_awk_p1": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "wrap_喊名_恍然",
              "state": "pending"
            }
          ],
          "next": "awk1_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n_climax_sig"
    },
    "awk1_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（那是……我自己亲口喊过名字的那点。）",
      "next": "awk1_2"
    },
    "awk1_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（那些名字……是喊魂。一路上就数我嗓门亮——是我自己，把它喊醒的。）",
      "next": "awk1_3"
    },
    "awk1_3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "脚帮那句话在耳朵里嗡嗡响：山里喊名，千万别应。应一声，魂就被勾了去。",
      "next": "awk1_sig"
    },
    "awk1_sig": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_看进山路",
            "signal": "hanming_awakening"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n_climax_sig"
    },
    "n_climax_sig": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_看进山路",
            "signal": "hanming_climax"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "cl_1"
    },
    "cl_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "喊声，停了。",
      "next": "cl_2"
    },
    "cl_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "换成了呼吸声。不远不近，吸气特别长——左边一口，右边一口，背后，一口。",
      "next": "cl_3"
    },
    "cl_3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（别应。咬住。别应——）",
      "next": "n_hold"
    },
    "n_hold": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "startPressureHold",
          "params": {
            "id": "forest_name_call"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "sw_outcome"
    },
    "sw_outcome": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "scenario_送货",
              "state": "answered",
              "reached": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "ans_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "ok_1"
    },
    "ok_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "不知过了多久——那几口呼吸，像在犹豫。",
      "next": "ok_2"
    },
    "ok_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "一缕极淡的香粉味，飘过。",
      "next": "ok_3"
    },
    "ok_3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "呼吸声退了。风声、虫鸣、夜鸟叫，一样一样地回来了。山里，重新有了正常的声音。",
      "next": "ok_4"
    },
    "ok_4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（别应……千万别应……）",
      "next": "n4"
    },
    "n4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "下到山脚，回头望——林子黑沉沉的，什么都没有。脚帮那句闲话，他算是亲身验过了：山里喊名，千万别应。",
      "next": "n5"
    },
    "n5": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（它凑近看了我一眼……认不准我是个啥子。——为啥子认不准？）",
      "next": "n_sig"
    },
    "n_sig": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_看进山路",
            "signal": "songhuo_returned"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "switchScene",
          "params": {
            "targetScene": "雾津街头",
            "targetSpawnPoint": "from_event"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "playScriptedDialogue",
          "params": {
            "lines": [
              {
                "speaker": "",
                "text": "回到城里，他给自己灌了二两烧酒。酒入喉是热的，后脖颈还是凉的。"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "ans_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "——「哎。」",
      "next": "ans_2"
    },
    "ans_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "字出口的一瞬，他自己都没反应过来。是嘴，自己应的。",
      "next": "ans_3"
    },
    "ans_3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "一切声音，骤停。比安静更安静。整座山，像把耳朵一齐竖了起来。",
      "next": "ans_4"
    },
    "ans_4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（跑——！）",
      "next": "n_escape"
    },
    "n_escape": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "startPressureHold",
          "params": {
            "id": "forest_escape_run"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "ans_5"
    },
    "ans_5": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "他不记得自己是怎么滚下最后一段坡的。冲出林子时，天刚泛起鱼肚白。他趴在地上，干呕。",
      "next": "ans_6"
    },
    "ans_6": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（我应了……我应了……为啥子要应……）",
      "next": "n_sig_ans"
    },
    "n_sig_ans": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_看进山路",
            "signal": "songhuo_returned"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "switchScene",
          "params": {
            "targetScene": "雾津街头",
            "targetSpawnPoint": "from_event"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "playScriptedDialogue",
          "params": {
            "lines": [
              {
                "speaker": "",
                "text": "回到城里，他给自己灌了四两烧酒。这回是热是凉，他没尝出来。那一声「哎」，在耳朵里转了一夜。"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
}
